name: Mini Purse - Leafy
description:
Petite and just right for business cards, lipgloss and small change.  Hand made in Sydney with cotton outer and inner lining, it closes with a lovely black snap button.

Measurements: 
♥ Length: 14cm
♥ Height: 11cm (folded)

† Please note that the pattern on the flap may vary slightly from the picture due to the fact that the pattern comes from a large piece of fabric design, however I can guarantee it will look just as gorgeous.

Pricing in Australian Dollars.

name: Card- Love
description:
Fly away with a heart balloon. Designed & printed with soluble ink on archival paper in Sydney. (Blank on the inside)

Comes with a white envelope to seal with a kiss and packed in a clear cello sleeve.

Pricing in Australian Dollars.
